title: dateDiff
name: dateDiff
description: Determines the number of given date parts between two different dates

arguments.name: datepart
arguments.description:
String that specifies the units in which to count:
- yyyy: Years
- q: Quarters
- m: Months
- y: Days of year (same as d)
- d: Days
- w: Weekdays (same as ww)
- ww: Weeks
- h: Hours
- n: Minutes
- s: Seconds
